His words tingled through her, both body & meta-processor. 

Smiling as her kissed her, she once again threw passion into it. No longer 
caring if it was too organic or not. It didn't matter any more.  

Now passionately returning that kiss as her form leaned against his, melting 
into his arms wrapped around her.

--part1_1cd.bf6682a.2c200fd0_boundary
